            . I was night officer - the prisoners were brought into the watch-house - I found this handkerchief in Figgins's pocket.</p>
               <p>Figgins's Defence. I was returning from the Surrey theatre - I found this handkerchief, and took it up - I came on and was taken.</p>
               <p>Sookin's Defence. I had been out with Rason from two o'clock - we were coming over the water, and a man came and took us.</p>
